=== EVENT_ALIEN_MONUMENT ===
# id: 38
# title: Alien Monument
# chinese_title: 外星纪念碑
# category: AlienContact
# mode: starmap

A colossal structure orbits a dead star — clearly artificial, impossibly old. Its surface is etched with symbols that tug at the edge of comprehension.

* [Dock and decipher the symbols]
  ~ gain_radical("大")
  解读 (jiědú) — decipher
* [Chip off a piece for analysis]
  ~ gain_scrap(12)
  分析 (fēnxī) — analyze
* [Broadcast a greeting toward the monument]
  ~ start_combat(3)
  问候 (wènhòu) — greeting
